   <div class="cmp-efe-plannerbio--aboutus">
       <h2 class="cmp-efe-plannerbio--aboutus__title">One of three headline options</h2>
       <div class="cmp-efe-plannerbio--aboutus__container">
           <div class="cmp-efe-plannerbio--aboutus__aboutme">
               <h3 class="cmp-efe-plannerbio--aboutus__aboutme--subtitle">About me</h3>
               <p>PERSONAL BLURB - Since 1992, I’ve been working with my clients as their dedicated financial planner. Together we discuss their lifelong hopes and dreams, then create a livable plan that can help keep them on track to reach every one of their goals. Outside of work, I enjoy spending time boating with my family. I also like trying new restaurants and exploring unique flavors.</p>
           </div>
           <div class="cmp-efe-plannerbio--aboutus__block">
               <div class="cmp-efe-plannerbio--aboutus__certification">
                   <h3 class="cmp-efe-plannerbio--aboutus__certification--subtitle">Certifications</h3>
                   <p>Full certification title 1</p>
                   <p>Full certification title 2</p>
                   <p>Full certification title 3</p>
               </div>
               <div class="cmp-efe-plannerbio--aboutus__education">
                   <h3 class="cmp-efe-plannerbio--aboutus__education--subtitle">Education</h3>
                   <p>Degree title, Institution name 1</p>
                   <p>Degree title, Institution name 2</p>
                   <p>Degree title, Institution name 3</p>
               </div>
           </div>
       </div>
       <div class="button cmp-efe-plannerbio--container__hero-text--cta cmp-button--button-primary cmp-button--unset cmp-button--default cmp-button--default cmp-efe-plannerbio--aboutus__cta">
           <button type="button" id="button-5487aab983" class="cmp-button" data-cmp-clickable="" data-cmp-data-layer="{&quot;button-5487aab983&quot;:{&quot;@type&quot;:&quot;core-components-examples/components/button&quot;,&quot;dc:title&quot;:&quot;Button&quot;}}">
